mesmerizing-optical-illusion-desk-toy,Mezmocoin Phantom- Mesmerizing optical illusion desk toy,"

Precision machined desk toy that seemingly defies gravity by presenting a transparent optical illusion.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption=""PATENT PENDING DESIGN"" data-id=""31213645"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

While rotating the middle part of the spinner visually disappears and is almost invisible to the naked eye. It creates a truly amusing optical effect which gave us a the idea to call it a ghost, a Optical Illusion Desk Toy.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31310803"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption=""Collection of three beautiful metals- Brass, Stainless steel and Coper."" data-id=""31176040"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">
<figcaption class=""px2"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">Collection of three beautiful metals- Brass, Stainless steel and Coper.</figcaption>

Since the middle part is asymmetrical it requires a mathematically calculated balancing that is hidden inside the Optical Illusion Desk Toy's body. The end result is an absolutely perfect and smooth rotation in both- fast and slow speeds.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31196306"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">
Spin it and let it glide above the surface of your desktop. The coin size shape makes it the perfect way to bring the magic with you.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31310907"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31176073"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

Optical Illusion Desk Toy will smoothly rotate on any desk or flat surface. Built for creators, makers, thinkers, and anyone who wants to release their inner creativity and imagination. Keep focus, relieve stress or simply play around anytime and anywhere.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31213258"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

You can easily spin it with a twist of fingers. The unique shape and smooth finish make it very pleasant to interact with. Optical Illusion Desk Toy spins silently so you won't be bothering anyone around.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31213167"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

Our record is almost 12 minutes with a single spin. Desk Toy which helps to achieve rotation times over 11 minutes on a glass surface. It is super easy to use- just place it in the center and pull the kevlar string. It will launch the Optical Illusion Desk Toy with an extreme acceleration.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31249569"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

The design team love spinning toys! The physics behind them are simply remarkable. Seeing a flat object balancing absolutely still on a tiny tip is just mesmerizing- like it would tend to defy gravity while rotating. The unique shape of Optical Illusion Desk Toy opens new possibilities. Spin on the edge, launch them together, compete with your friends and more.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31249589"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31176082"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">
The flat shape and compact size makes it a perfect toy to carry around. It will fit in any pocket without making a bulk.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31176090"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

Want to surprise someone? No matter the age, Optical Illusion Desk Toy makes a truly great and original present that creates a bit of magic every time you interact with it. Each unit is crafted with attention to the smallest detail and built to last a lifetime.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31249839"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

Optical Illusion Desk Toy consists out of three minutely machined metal parts carefully pressed together. With our CNC machines, The design team are able to achieve such level of precision that is rarely found in regular everyday objects. You’ll instantly notice minutely milled lines and smooth surface texture upon touching Optical Illusion Desk Toy for the first time!Each Optical Illusion Desk Toy hides a mathematically calculated and precision machined balancing process unnoticeable from the outside. The end result is an absolutely smooth and long rotation without any wobbling even in slow speeds.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31249028"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

The design team have gone through multiple prototyping processes to achieve the best end result. With each of our desk toys The design team challenge ourselves to create a one of a kind piece of machinery that you wouldn't find anywhere else. Optical Illusion Desk Toy is no exception!
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31250033"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

To create the transparent optical effect while rotating The design team needed to design the inside space as hollow as possible. Therefore Optical Illusion Desk Toy has only a single connection between the center and the outside ring. It looks amazing though it makes the shape asymmetric which requires an additional balancing solution.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31278098"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">
Additionally you will be able to get the custom leather sleeve to protect the PHANTOM and carry it with style. The sleeve will be available via surveys after the project ends.
<div class=""template asset"" data-alt-text="""" data-caption="""" data-id=""31248819"" contenteditable=""false"" data-mce-fragment=""1"">

column19: >
>With the 3 different sizes, you can truly customize it to you for every position, and allow you to learn new ways to use the wheel to assist you in your practice.

column1: The majority of exercises will be fine. You might find it slightly too big for one or two exercises. That said, a couple of my friends are your height and have no problems with the size. Hope this helps.
2. WOULD THIS BE SUITABLE FOR SOMEONE WITH KYPHOSIS? I DO YOGA BUT HAVE TROUBLE WITH BACKBENDS BECAUSE OF THE CURVATURE IN MY SPINE.

I would especially recommend it for someone with kyphosis! A yoga wheel may be exactly what you need to ease into more comfortable Backbends in Your practice. As long as your safe, go slow and listen to your body it could help your spine greatly. Having said that know I'm Not a doctor or chiropractor so depends on the severity and specifics of your condition you may want to double-check if you feel it necessary. Great question!!
3. IS THIS AS EFFECTIVE AS USING AN INFLATABLE GYM BALL TO ASSIST AND PRACTICE BACKBENDS? THANKS FOR YOUR TIME.

I've never tried to use a ball to assist me with backbends but I can tell you that the wheel has helped me get a lot deeper I am now able to do a with one leg off the ground and I can also do a forearm backbend and there was no way to get there without the wheel for me.
4. HOW THICK IS THE FOAM PADDING?
Hi, it is a comfortable 1/4 inch.

professional-boning-knife,Professional Boning Knife,<h3><strong>A Perfect Blend Of Modern Technology &amp
Hand-forged by professional Blacksmiths from high-quality steel, the perfect blade for all your indoors &

Crafted from High Carbon 5Cr15MoV Stainless Steel. To boost its sturdiness, the steel contains 0.45 - 0.5 carbon. This gives the blade improved tensile strength, edge retention, and overall resistance to wear.

column2: Superior Corrosion Resistance. Ultra-sharp edge comes with a Rockwell Hardness Scale of 55-57 which makes it among the toughest knives in its class.
Narrow Blade. This knife's curved blade makes separating meat from the bone a breeze. Perfect for trimming brisket, skinning or breaking down a whole chicken, or even separating ribs from the loin.

column1: Ergonomic Handle Design. These knives feature an ergonomic handle design that makes them super easy and comfortable to use. They are also very well balanced allowing for superior control and stability when cutting. This minimizes the risk of accidents when using them.
Why Is It Important To Have A Sharp Knife?

A sharp knife is safer. A sharp blade is predictable. when it strikes or is drawn across the food's surface, it won't slip. This makes it easy to control how the blade moves through the food, giving you control over your chopping or slicing. A dull blade will slip, which makes control difficult and increases the risk that it will slip into your finger. With a dull knife, it's only a matter of time until you slip while applying more pressure.

A sharp knife works better. Sharp knives need less brute force to cut than dull knives. Less brute force means less damage to the food, which you can easily see by looking closely at the cut. A sharp knife helps in maintaining the texture of your ingredients. Delicate ingredients, like herbs, will look fresher longer if you slice through them cleanly, whereas a dull knife will crush more of the cells surrounding the cut, which ultimately accelerates wilting and discoloration.
But most importantly, a dull knife slows you down, while a sharp knife makes prep easier and more enjoyable.

Features of the Wooden Balance Toy:

• EASY AND FUN: A fun game that brings the family together and is an exceptional screen-free play option. Done balancing one side? Try balancing upside-down! It’s an exciting balance toy that challenges kids, students, and entire families!
  • STIMULATING TOY: Wooden Balance Toy is the unpredictably fun coordination and focuses game for your children, students, the whole family! Wooden Balance Toy helps kids and adults improve they're fine motor skills, increase concentration, and develop stronger critical thinking skills.
  • SENSORY TOY: Stimulate your senses by improving fine motor skills and hand-eye coordination. This coordination balance game relieves stress by requiring focus and attention. Wooden Balance Toy is great for autism or autistic children and other kids and toddlers that need help with hand-eye coordination, sensory and/or fine motor skills
  • AWARD-WINNING STEM TOY: Winner of the Creative Kids 2018 Toy of the Year, it will meet your needs for both entertainment and education. Developed in cooperation with occupational and physiotherapists
  • DESIGNED TO LAST: Wooden Balance Toy is a quality built, European design, the toy that will stand up to any punishment you can dish out. Product Siz: 7.25 inches x 1.69 inches x 1.69 inches US Patent: 8,936,536.

>How to Set Up Easily In 5 Steps
>1. Secure the display and IR light on the optical sight with the pipe clamp
>2. Loosen the plastic screws (totally eight), and centrally fix the connecting tube in the rear of the eyepiece of the optical sight
>3. Turn on the machine and rotate the lens of the machine (inside the tube) to adjust the focus, and adjust the cross line of optical sight to be clear.
>4. Adjust the position of the connecting tube, and tighten the screws till the cross line in the centre of the display. And the commissioning of the machine is complete till now

>5. In the future application, if the image is blurred caused by the different distances of the objects, the image clarity shall be adjusted by side focus roller (and the parallax adjustment roller) attached with the optical sight. Do not move the machine lens, otherwise the cross line will be blurry

column3: >The portable submersible oil pump has stable performance and is completely sealed and insulated.

column1: Lightweight, easy to install, and carry.
The wire is 3 meters long and the pump port diameter is 16 mm.
Suitable for large harvesters, agricultural machinery, construction machinery, large-wheeled tractors, etc.
Using DC12V direct current motor, low noise, fast speed. It has good sealing performance and adopts multiple seals to prevent leakage and prolong service life.
The stainless steel shell increases the thickness of the shell, makes the shell stronger, not easy to deform, and can effectively prevent the shell from rust and rot.

There is a stainless steel filter in the bottom filter of the oil well pump to make the diesel oil (or water) pumped out cleaner. The bottom filter is equipped with a threaded interface, which is convenient for disassembly, maintenance, and replacement. Can achieve the purpose of repeated use.
There is a midway switch on the power cord for easy operation. The oil output is about 12L/min. After use, the oil well pump should be taken out of the oil (or water) in time.
When pumping oil, you should first connect the self-prepared oil outlet hose, and then put the whole oil well into clean oil (or water).

column2: >Never run out of power in emergency or power-off situations

column1: Afraid of being with a dead cell phone and no power?
If the answer is yes, then we have the solution! Simply plug in your device to the USB port to charge, suitable for all phones and power banks wherever you are.
Dead batteries in the middle of nowhere?

Charge up your device with this generator! Small and compact with a detachable handle for easy storage, the K-POWER™ Emergency Crank Generator is an absolute must for your bug out bag, home emergency kit, or outdoor recreation.
Incredibly simple to use, this is the best hand crank generator you will find.
Forgot to charge that powerbank when the power goes out?

Hey, we've all been there. Simply attach it to your K-POWER™ Emergency Crank Generator and have the ability to generate power in the most remote areas or when there is a power outage in the most convenient and practical way. Works with any USB device.
Need a USB charger in an emergency?
The USB port also can be used as a power source to attach a mini USB light, fan, or any other USB powered device. Fully adjustable to match the required corresponding voltage output.
Tired of cheap plastic that breaks as soon as you look at it?

The K-POWER™ Emergency Crank Generator is made of far hardier stuff than the cheap plastic you find on most sites. A full metal outer casing combined with anti-slip foot pads provides a sturdy and firm standing for this portable hand crank generator, combined with an easy crank to provide effortless and time-saving manual power generation.
Package Includes: 1 x K-POWER™ Emergency Crank Generator

• 【New Inverted Design】 This folding umbrella adopts reverse design. The wet surface of the umbrella will be inside with the dry surface exposed when you close it, which greatly prevents water dropping down and keeps your clothes, floor and car dry. What's more, you can open this inverted umbrella easily in your car and will not get wet.

• 【Superior Windproof and Waterproof】 This umbrella is flexible enough to withstand powerful wind without turning inside out. It is fortified with 8 reinforced fiberglass ribs. The cannopy is made of high density 210T waterproof material which makes it good at waterproof function. Besides it is 46 inch arc, you don't have to choose between gigantic windproof umbrellas or tiny ones that cannot provide minimal wind protection.

• 【Reflective Stripe Design and Safer】 The inverted umbrella is surrounded by reflective stripes, which offers 360° high visibility. The reflective stripe delivers high visibility during low light and rainy conditions to alert cars and vehicles, for extra safety in low visibility conditions, important for children, pedestrians and commuters, you will be safer when walk in dark and rain.

Gently Auto Open/Close by one hand

Just push the button once to automatically open and press again to instantly fold the canopy closed. You do not need to wait another second to open the umbrella when you get out of your car in the rain, especially in heavy rainfall, even when your hands are full of things.


Light Weight and Compact Design

This umbrella folds itself into an ultra small size which is only 11.8 inches in length when close,and the weight is 12.5 oz, a truly handy and portable umbrella.It is compact enough to perfectly fits into purse, handbag and backpack and more.

Heavy Duty Windproof Umbrella

Reinforced durable fiberglass ribs gives it unbeatable flexibility and strength. It is strong enough to withstand powerful gust without turning inside-out or even hurt yourself. Using our reverse umbrella, you will get best protection in windy days.

How to Use

1.Unlock the Umbrella and shake it gently.

2.Hold the handle and press the button, it will open automatically.

3.Press the button again,it closes automatically.

4.Holding the handle with one hand and holding the top of the umbrella with the other hand, you need push both ends towards the center until it clicks to lock the umbrella.

column3: >When we drink canned drinks, we usually can't open the lid and even break the handle ring or hurt our hands, it's annoying. Introducing <strong>Mintimlâ„?/strong&gt
column4: Can Opener, a bar tool designed to help safely remove the top of almost any can with leaving no sharp edges. No more hurting and laborious, enhancing our drinking experience.

column1:
Create A Smooth Pour Drink
The locking mechanism securely locks the cutting wheel in place to ensure a consistent cut and reduced strain on our hands. And removing the top of the can allows us to pour and enjoy the drink without interruption.

Fits Almost Any Can
Mintiml™ Can Opener can be used on most 8-19 oz beverage cans, such as the canned wine, canned cocktails, energy drinks, iced coffee, soda/seltzer, and other canned drinks. Just enjoy your cold drink anytime and anywhere!

Enjoy A Full Drink Taste
Never afraid of the grip hook was snapped or even cut your fingers and mouth. Just own Mintimlâ„?Can Opener and open cans with ease in seconds! Removing the entire top allows our nose to enjoy the full taste of the beverage just like a glass cup.

DIY Your Drinks As Your Flavor
By removing the entire top of the can, it allows us to add supplementary spices to our favorite canned drinks easier. Whether you like to mix it with soda pop or just add a little citrus in your beer, it's all available. Also, you can take advantage of an empty can to arrange and plant flowers, or as a pen container,  just get your imagination started!

column1: • Does that uncomfortable pillow keep you up all night? You fold it, flip it, and fluff it, but it's never quite right, not anymore, now there's All-round Sleep Pillow, a thick pillow that's shaped like a small handful of eggs with a groove for your head in the center, which is so comfortable and supportive

column3: >If you can't use it, we will give you a full refund!

column1:
Soft and Comfortable Auxiliary Pillow
With All-round Sleep Pillow, you'll be more likely to feel as if you've set it down on a soft cloud of comfortable material that can support your head, neck, and shoulders throughout the night.

Supportive Egg Groove Design
Resulted in the groove in the center it holds and supports your head and neck at an ideal height for sleep. Meanwhile, the higher curves that surround this groove will help keep your head and neck in this ideal position so they don't wiggle about and become stiff or sore.
Breathable to Have A Cool and Dry Sleep

This Sleep Pillow is so well-ventilated that it won't make you hot and sweaty while you sleep. You may not feel the urgent need to hurry to the shower and wash off excess sweat if that's something you normally do.

Fits Any Sleeping Position
It's not necessary that you stay on your back, as the pillow will accommodate side sleepers and stomach sleepers, too. After you've laid down and chosen your sleeping position, the pillow will begin to gently conform to the shape of your head and upper body.

Lie Down For Sound Sleep
All-round Sleep Pillow will cradle and support your head and neck by evenly dispersing the weight of those body parts throughout your entire pillow. For virtually all sleepers, this will enhance your comfort level as you sleep, and thereby help you sleep soundly.
1. Put it in a pillowcase
2. Position the pillow on your bed
3. Lie down and place your head into the round groove in its center.
